ilUrl>/RXLImages/7/SORR-98hotel_Guest_Room_4_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>60</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>80</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/7/SORR-98hotel_Guest_Room_5.jpg</Url><Width>240</Width><Height>360</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/SORR-98hotel_Guest_Room_5_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>60</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>80</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Gently nested in the hills surrounding Sorrento, Hotel Colli San Pietro ***, offers its guests the opportunity to experience a relaxing stay, dived in the green hills of the sorrentine peninsula and the blue Gulfs of Naples and Salerno, just a few steps from the Amalfi Coast and its renowned sea pearls.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The Hotel is placed on the main road between Positano and Sorrento, far from the crowds of the city centres at the sea, overlooking the green hills and exposed to the fresh breeze of the hills during the hot summertime.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>All rooms, colored with different leitmotivs, are provided with a private bathroom with shower, air conditioning, TV LCD, hairdryer and safe.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>The Hotel is located in front of the bus station on the line between Meta and Amalfi by which you can easily reach all places of the Amalfi Coast and the Circumvesuviana Railway in direction of Pompeji, Herculaneum and Naples where you can discover the art works left from the Kings that governed the Kingdom of the Two Sicilies, without forgetting Caserta with its Royal Palace and the mount Vesuvius that you can climb up to the crater</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>The Restaurant Colli San Pietro offers an excellent typical cuisine, based on local produces of the area, which origin and quality is taken care of by a renowned chef of the place. In the evening, you also can choose to have a real neapolitan Pizza, that we prepare in the traditional wood-oven. If you like to have pizza at lunch, please ask us and we will do our best to fullfil your wish.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>The reception area is small,but very elegant</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>InHouseBar</Code><Text>Hotel bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PetsAllowed</Code><Text>Pets allowed</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarRentDesk</Code><Text>Car rental desk</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Restaurant</Code><Text>Restaurant</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Garage</Code><Text>Garage</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Babysitter</Code><Text>Babysitter</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Entertainment</Code><Text>Entertainment</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MultilingualStaff</Code><Text>Multilingual Staff</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>30</Score><Description>Three star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>